{"word":"Abinadab","slug":"abinadab","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abinadab</b> <a href=\"#/H41\">H41</a> <br/> 1. A Levite, in whose house the ark of God rested twenty years<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=2'>1Sa 7:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=4'>2Sa 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=7'>1Ch 13:7</a><br/> 2. Son of Jesse<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=8'>1Sa 16:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=13'>1Sa 17:13</a><br/> 3. Called Ishui, son of Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=49'>1Sa 14:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=2'>1Sa 31:2</a><br/> 4. Father of one of Solomon's purveyors, called Ben-abinadab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=11'>1Ki 4:11</a>"}]}